don't forget to include jquery.min.js
===>include scroll.js in your script tags to get things working
steps to use the sticky header js file in your code
1.wrap your header into a class called 'header-container';
2.'fixed-header' class will be added to the header-container classed div when the page has scrolled down by 100px
3.In your css add class 'fixed-header' and make it position:fixed and apply styling to it,according to what's required
 
